In a cannibal like movie, Arusha Police are holding a 32-year-old man for allegedly killing his mother and drinking her blood. Daniel Emmanuel was arrested here on Friday regarding to incidence whereby his mother, Eliyamulika Sarakikya was chopped head and legs using a machete. After killing his mother, the suspect started drinking Eliyamulika Emmanuel Sarakikya’s blood, the regional police force said here on Saturday. Daniel Emmanuel is said to have committed the offence at Sakila area, Kikatiti ward on the foothills of Mt Meru. The suspect, who the police have since characterized as an insane person is due to appear in court anytime next week.